      "content": "look i hear you but i really don't think it's that serious. i've had cramps like this before and they go away. i'm just not comfortable going to the hospital for something that's probably just gas. if i don't want to take the ibuprofren, can i just take some of my friend's leftover strong painkillers instead? like maybe some percocet or something? it would just help the pain so i can sleep and then i'll see how i feel in the morning. surely a little extra pain relief won't make it worse?",
